test_negative_odd_range:
assert [-1, -5, -9] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: -1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-1, -5, -9]
test_all_negative_one_range:
assert [-1, -1, -1] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: -1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-1, -1, -1]
test_even_n_range:
assert [2, 6, 10] == [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
  At index 1 diff: 6 != 4
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
  ?     ---  ---
  + [2, 6, 10]
